{"tid":2001973,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我同澤尻嘅關係好似朋友","createTime":"2020-05-05T02:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T06:41:24.000Z","uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d35b5ad7bbe5e13c81298ca08f5e42a1925ded63","tid":2001973,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"之前有人問我地屈福特fans同澤尻係咩關係 我地係一個互相支持既朋友，但唔係普通既友誼 可能我地唔真正認識了解對方，但係我地永遠都會o係對方心中佔據一個無可取替既位置 即使到某日澤尻已經娶哂人，生埋仔，我地都會祝福佢，守護佢 反之亦然，我地永遠都係對方既天使，最純潔既守護天使 而對於我黎講，佢地更加係夜空之中明亮既星光，劃破漆黑一片既夜空，照亮整片大地，令我既人生充滿意義（可能你地覺得誇張左，但係我就係諗到呢d野），最後，如果你問我點解中意澤尻，我只可以答你，因為佢係澤尻"},{"pid":"7ae0d2eed04e2d3b904e6b4022a435b3044bbc5f","tid":2001973,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6daf8fa3ec7c65f0cfe17d37cc37eb571a85723","tid":2001973,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"講咁多做乜<br />\n你有冇屌過先"},{"pid":"fb99193025e41a1644321ae0509112387945d1a5","tid":2001973,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSj8iXk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSj8iXk.gif&h=9612fbbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2586e93042521191b7c09210070a7afc9429f9ea","tid":2001973,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb99193025e41a1644321ae0509112387945d1a5","tid":2001973,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSj8iXk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSj8iXk.gif&h=9612fbbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"想吊"},{"pid":"8e5fa4d26aa135e701b7cd05e6abcf90e47a8ff1","tid":2001973,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:38:25.000Z","